  "content": "\n \n \n  <ne-clipboard source=\"https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yuque.com%2Fqone%2Fyys%2Fcgdd0a2g5wg4ka9m\"></ne-clipboard>\n  <section nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/02230acf-8dec-466d-1bdd-134eafe59500/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42592592592592593\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" width=\"1800\" data-imgfileid=\"501967757\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/02230acf-8dec-466d-1bdd-134eafe59500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <blockquote style=\"padding:16px 20px;color:rgb(80, 80, 80);visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:18px;border-color:initial;line-height:1.64;box-sizing:border-box !important;quotes:none;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:4px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;margin-top:20px;border-width:initial;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:20px;border-style:none;\">\n   <p style=\"max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;visibility: visible;text-align: left;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">「有意思小周刊」是我利用零碎时间，梳理记录一周的日常阅读与思考内容。目的是为以后更好构建自己知识体系，也为了将这些内容分享给你。</span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(1, 194, 96);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">以下是这期值得关注的内容</span></strong></span></h3>\n  <h3 style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">📰 推荐阅读</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">1.Manus刷爆圈儿，平心而谈，产品经理到底应该怎么拥抱AI？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">2.探索AI工具幕后，打造你自己的Agent应用</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">3.这才是真正的用户分层，而不是看平均数</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">4.利用 AI 提升设计</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">5.思考：设计好产品为什么要顺应大脑的奖赏系统？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">6.UI设计中的B端和C端差异(2025新版)</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">7.货拉拉大模型应用开发体系演进与实践</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">8.界面的设计感，应该怎么练？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">9.ToB 场景下用户需求挖掘与产品共创</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">10.LSM-TREE从入门到入魔：从零开始实现一个高性能键值存储 ｜ 得物技术</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">11.万字详解零售支付：支付全景、渠道聚合、支付中台、进件与配置</span></p>\n  <h4 style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">🔎&nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">发现新大陆</span></strong></span></h4>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-indent: 0em;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <ne-clipboard data=\"%7B%22type%22%3A%22fragment%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22%23fragment%22%2C%22children%22%3A%5B%7B%22type%22%3A%22element%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ua2c24766%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22oli%22%2C%22attrs%22%3A%7B%22list%22%3A%22ub47f0dcc%22%2C%22indexType%22%3A0%2C%22indexStyle%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22fid%22%3A%22ud7c9b7eb%22%2C%22parentIndex%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22index%22%3A0%7D%2C%22children%22%3A%5B%7B%22type%22%3A%22text%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u93513643%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22%23text%22%2C%22attrs%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22data%22%3A%22Seafile%EF%BC%9A%E5%BC%80%E6%BA%90%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E4%BA%91%E7%9B%98%22%7D%5D%7D%2C%7B%22type%22%3A%22element%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u7ae35382%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22oli%22%2C%22attrs%22%3A%7B%22list%22%3A%22ub47f0dcc%22%2C%22indexType%22%3A0%2C%22indexStyle%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22fid%22%3A%22ud7c9b7eb%22%2C%22parentIndex%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22index%22%3A1%7D%2C%22children%22%3A%5B%7B%22type%22%3A%22text%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ucea29975%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22%23text%22%2C%22attrs%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22data%22%3A%22Monaspace%EF%BC%9AGitHub%20%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E7%AD%89%E5%AE%BD%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93%22%7D%5D%7D%2C%7B%22type%22%3A%22element%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u9c274fe5%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22oli%22%2C%22attrs%22%3A%7B%22list%22%3A%22ub47f0dcc%22%2C%22indexType%22%3A0%2C%22indexStyle%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22fid%22%3A%22ud7c9b7eb%22%2C%22parentIndex%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22index%22%3A2%7D%2C%22children%22%3A%5B%7B%22type%22%3A%22text%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ub713fd8b%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22%23text%22%2C%22attrs%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22data%22%3A%221000%20%E4%B8%AA%E7%88%86%E6%AC%BE%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98%22%7D%5D%7D%5D%2C%22attrs%22%3A%7B%7D%7D\" source=\"https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yuque.com%2Fqone%2Fyys%2Fzc184gir1qx4ldwk%23YHgv6\"></ne-clipboard>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\">1.一个专门收录分享免费 DeepSeek / API 的网站：DeepSeek 导航网</span></span></p>\n  <h4 style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: 1.6em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">🎯 言论·语录</span></span></strong></h4>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-indent: 0em;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <ne-clipboard data=\"%7B%22type%22%3A%22fragment%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22%23fragment%22%2C%22children%22%3A%5B%7B%22type%22%3A%22element%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uad39aad0%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22oli%22%2C%22attrs%22%3A%7B%22list%22%3A%22u1f9aab83%22%2C%22indexType%22%3A0%2C%22indexStyle%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22fid%22%3A%22ua8b54bf8%22%2C%22parentIndex%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22index%22%3A0%7D%2C%22children%22%3A%5B%7B%22type%22%3A%22text%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uf19cff7a%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22%23text%22%2C%22attrs%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22data%22%3A%22%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E9%87%8F%E8%AF%84%E4%BC%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%9B%E7%A7%8D%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%22%7D%5D%7D%2C%7B%22type%22%3A%22element%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u2c12aa1a%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22oli%22%2C%22attrs%22%3A%7B%22list%22%3A%22u1f9aab83%22%2C%22indexType%22%3A0%2C%22indexStyle%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22fid%22%3A%22ua8b54bf8%22%2C%22parentIndex%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22index%22%3A1%7D%2C%22children%22%3A%5B%7B%22type%22%3A%22text%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u71de6e6d%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22%23text%22%2C%22attrs%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22data%22%3A%22%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%9C%E8%A5%BF%E8%A6%81%E4%BA%B2%E8%87%AA%E9%A2%84%E6%BC%94%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%22%7D%5D%7D%5D%2C%22attrs%22%3A%7B%7D%7D\" source=\"https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yuque.com%2Fqone%2Fyys%2Fzc184gir1qx4ldwk%23YHgv6\"></ne-clipboard>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">1.晚点独家丨美团内部沟通会：食杂零售、国际化、AI 是王兴关注的 “新” 方向</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">2.面试玄学？技术招聘反直觉定律：面试问题数量与offer概率成反比</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\">3.DeepSeek来了，我们这个行业会不会被淘汰</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: 1.6em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">📚 近期书单</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 0em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\">1.《县委书记们的主政谋略》：揭秘县官的目标与内心世界</span></span></p>\n  <p data-track=\"34\" style=\"visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:18px;border-color:initial;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;max-width:100%;margin-top:20px;border-width:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0em;border-style:initial;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/eb439603-efbe-4cfc-4a45-649e4a9d9300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.11296296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"text-align: center;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;width: 578px;height: 65px;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"65\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/eb439603-efbe-4cfc-4a45-649e4a9d9300/public\"></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span leaf=\"\">▌</span><span leaf=\"\">Manus刷爆圈儿，平心而谈，产品经理到底应该怎么拥抱AI？</span></span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span><span leaf=\"\"><a style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzk1Nzc1NjM1NA==&amp;mid=2247499326&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=f14a00d7abc8010884ca0566289c7146&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzk1Nzc1NjM1NA==&amp;mid=2247499326&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=f14a00d7abc8010884ca0566289c7146&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" data-itemshowtype=\"undefined\" target=\"_blank\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/If-kXk_Av-l4CZc_fYqFcw</a></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">文章探讨了产品经理如何正确拥抱AI。建议先进行系统层面的粗浅学习，建立整体印象，再结合业务和兴趣进行单点突破，通过实践完善技能。强调实践的重要性，认为在AI浪潮中，产品经理的核心竞争力在于用户洞察力，而非单纯依赖AI工具。未来，洞察力将成为产品经理的核心高地，助力创造真正满足用户需求的产品。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzk1Nzc1NjM1NA==&amp;mid=2247499326&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=f14a00d7abc8010884ca0566289c7146&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" imgurl=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/g0kpxARkI2SVlPVPibKEXK5jfVLxGOicd4FjMbGhDI4x44euhTDTvG5iaTU1KxiaKzMyQYopLyLqOia3nxFDcL3JlJw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" linktype=\"image\" tab=\"innerlink\" data-itemshowtype=\"undefined\" target=\"_blank\" data-linktype=\"1\"><span class=\"js_jump_icon h5_image_link\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f0b031de-a2fd-495e-0084-bdf1a19eb500/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5928338762214984\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"614\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"501967759\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f0b031de-a2fd-495e-0084-bdf1a19eb500/public\"></span></a>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);font-size: 18px;\"><span leaf=\"\">▌</span><span leaf=\"\">探索AI工具幕后，打造你自己的Agent应用</span></span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span><span leaf=\"\">https://tech.qimao.com/build-your-command-agent-tool/</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">文章介绍了如何打造一个智能命令行工具——Commander，通过AI技术实现输入指令、推理决策和执行操作的Agent应用。文中讲解了Agent的基本概念、实现原理和开发过程，并提供了配套代码。同时，还探讨了如何通过Prompt设计、模型选择和工具调用提升Agent的智能性和实用性。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6268f409-993e-47da-d95a-8fe501cd5000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.40553745928338764\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"614\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"501967760\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6268f409-993e-47da-d95a-8fe501cd5000/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span leaf=\"\">▌</span><span leaf=\"\">这才是真正的用户分层，而不是看平均数</span></span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span><span leaf=\"\"><a style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzOTM0NDQxNA==&amp;mid=2247547030&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b5143b040bcbbe5e058697b45508b70f&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzOTM0NDQxNA==&amp;mid=2247547030&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b5143b040bcbbe5e058697b45508b70f&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" data-itemshowtype=\"undefined\" target=\"_blank\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/SH7fI721R1KotSR8wTxIoQ</a></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">用户分层是数据分析中的重要环节，不能仅依赖平均数来划分。通过多维度分析，如消费金额、购买频次、毛利等，结合业务特点，可以精准定位核心用户群体，从而制定针对性的运营策略。分层后，还需结合竞争对手情况，优化回馈比例，提升用户忠诚度和消费力。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzOTM0NDQxNA==&amp;mid=2247547030&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b5143b040bcbbe5e058697b45508b70f&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" imgurl=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/g0kpxARkI2SVlPVPibKEXK5jfVLxGOicd4N8SM2ftScmN9W9U6NhynzicedF0SsA4zFNf5HgbXBMdHCnNqx7RZh7g/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" linktype=\"image\" tab=\"innerlink\" data-itemshowtype=\"undefined\" target=\"_blank\" data-linktype=\"1\"><span class=\"js_jump_icon h5_image_link\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ab2e7462-f227-40c6-607d-fe7e94cd5700/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7869674185463659\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"399\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"501967761\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ab2e7462-f227-40c6-607d-fe7e94cd5700/public\"></span></a>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span leaf=\"\">▌</span><span leaf=\"\">利用 AI 提升设计</span></span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span><span leaf=\"\"><a style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMjU0NTQ3Mg==&amp;mid=2247730611&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=1776a66c48c89351ed3e797cfb156394&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMjU0NTQ3Mg==&amp;mid=2247730611&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=1776a66c48c89351ed3e797cfb156394&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" data-itemshowtype=\"undefined\" target=\"_blank\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/LtVvUIL9GFSIwSlpdfp0zQ</a></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">文章探讨了 AI 在设计领域的应用与价值，指出 AI 虽无法完全取代设计师的创造力，但能作为强大工具助力设计工作。在平面设计和 UX/UI 设计中，AI 可生成图像、界面等基础元素，设计师需在此基础上进行个性化修改。文章还介绍了多款 AI 设计工具和 Figma 插件，强调 AI 能提升设计效率，拓展设计师的职业边界，鼓励设计师积极探索 AI 时代的设计机遇。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMjU0NTQ3Mg==&amp;mid=2247730611&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=1776a66c48c89351ed3e797cfb156394&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" imgurl=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/g0kpxARkI2SVlPVPibKEXK5jfVLxGOicd4wWml3rCuHyXkjWPDRbuy6Nq0m4SgXZDnHxpkrBZqCk00hKLe97YXQw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" linktype=\"image\" tab=\"innerlink\" data-itemshowtype=\"undefined\" target=\"_blank\" data-linktype=\"1\"><span class=\"js_jump_icon h5_image_link\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2b04c905-93d8-4766-ecc9-8ae5c501c600/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5602605863192183\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"614\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"501967762\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2b04c905-93d8-4766-ecc9-8ae5c501c600/public\"></span></a>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span leaf=\"\">▌</span><span leaf=\"\">思考：设计好产品为什么要顺应大脑的奖赏系统？</span></span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span><span leaf=\"\"><a style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzk0MTI1MDA2NA==&amp;mid=2247490161&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=75a2aa5f6a933400952a6f1b9e0187cc&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzk0MTI1MDA2NA==&amp;mid=2247490161&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=75a2aa5f6a933400952a6f1b9e0187cc&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" data-itemshowtype=\"undefined\" target=\"_blank\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/RmwCVaZPjW361VVBFZvg1g</a></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">设计好产品需要顺应大脑的奖赏系统，因为这一机制深刻影响人类行为。从基础的即时满足，到反思后的自我调整，再到追求更高层次的需求，奖赏系统贯穿其中。顺应它不仅能引导用户行为，还能在商业领域实现“科技向善”，帮助用户构建“数字免疫力”，推动产品成为提升生活品质和促进个人成长的助力。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzk0MTI1MDA2NA==&amp;mid=2247490161&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=75a2aa5f6a933400952a6f1b9e0187cc&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" imgurl=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/g0kpxARkI2SVlPVPibKEXK5jfVLxGOicd4nwAXPuVrQDGmRR34zflBucZicphxDETWmqpSBibN8IMaQ0JARDusB7lA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" linktype=\"image\" tab=\"innerlink\" data-itemshowtype=\"undefined\" target=\"_blank\" data-linktype=\"1\"><span class=\"js_jump_icon h5_image_link\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b3734560-85e2-47fe-7f5f-71a69d4acd00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.504424778761062\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"452\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"501967763\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b3734560-85e2-47fe-7f5f-71a69d4acd00/public\"></span></a>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span leaf=\"\">▌</span><span leaf=\"\">UI设计中的B端和C端差异(2025新版)</span></span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span><span leaf=\"\"><a style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI0Njc5NzM5OQ==&amp;mid=2247502270&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=218c3e770f48d74d82517e7a2621cbd8&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI0Njc5NzM5OQ==&amp;mid=2247502270&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=218c3e770f48d74d82517e7a2621cbd8&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" data-itemshowtype=\"undefined\" target=\"_blank\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/IHwFLbEYZ8Y0EMfREZFbng</a></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">UI设计中的B端和C端存在显著差异。B端设计面向商业用户，注重降本增效，强调功能性和操作效率，视觉和交互设计相对简洁实用。C端设计则面向普通消费者，以满足用户需求、提升体验和实现盈利为目标，更注重视觉效果、交互体验和品牌调性。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI0Njc5NzM5OQ==&amp;mid=2247502270&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=218c3e770f48d74d82517e7a2621cbd8&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" imgurl=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/g0kpxARkI2SVlPVPibKEXK5jfVLxGOicd4f7icT3vaziaYXO8nZRdYclkjdb7K69ibOAN8M3VswnTIzrTbtdhgn4PibQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" linktype=\"image\" tab=\"innerlink\" data-itemshowtype=\"undefined\" target=\"_blank\" data-linktype=\"1\"><span class=\"js_jump_icon h5_image_link\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5e037de1-01bd-4184-9f89-ccf67c325b00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5667752442996743\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"614\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"501967764\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5e037de1-01bd-4184-9f89-ccf67c325b00/public\"></span></a>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span leaf=\"\">▌</span><span leaf=\"\">货拉拉大模型应用开发体系演进与实践</span></span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span><span leaf=\"\"><a style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI0MjIxNjE0OQ==&amp;mid=2247505232&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=7ffddbc2da2dd981827fe112929da7f5&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI0MjIxNjE0OQ==&amp;mid=2247505232&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=7ffddbc2da2dd981827fe112929da7f5&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" data-itemshowtype=\"undefined\" target=\"_blank\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/9TIfKFAXbYaUEnPZPoWJ8w</a></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">货拉拉通过打造悟空平台，解决了大模型应用开发中的数据、场景和落地难题。平台构建了多模态知识引擎，统一处理文本、图像、视频等数据，提升了企业知识管理效率。同时，自研Agent Workflow智能引擎支持动态编排和多智能体协作，实现复杂业务流程的灵活定制。目前，该平台已在多个业务场景落地，显著提升了运营效率。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI0MjIxNjE0OQ==&amp;mid=2247505232&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=7ffddbc2da2dd981827fe112929da7f5&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" imgurl=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/g0kpxARkI2SVlPVPibKEXK5jfVLxGOicd4K7CLHrAUcpmDhFAVVKmia59dWdVOF7zOeUchRjuSG7DjKXUpb7oYu4w/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" linktype=\"image\" tab=\"innerlink\" data-itemshowtype=\"undefined\" target=\"_blank\" data-linktype=\"1\"><span class=\"js_jump_icon h5_image_link\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/65542899-9169-47f2-7bba-5c2e7301eb00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5407166123778502\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"614\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"501967765\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/65542899-9169-47f2-7bba-5c2e7301eb00/public\"></span></a>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span leaf=\"\">▌</span><span leaf=\"\">界面的设计感，应该怎么练？</span></span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span><span leaf=\"\"><a style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI0Njc5NzM5OQ==&amp;mid=2247502202&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=e52e1824dcf3fd441be4cd8486b9e354&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI0Njc5NzM5OQ==&amp;mid=2247502202&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=e52e1824dcf3fd441be4cd8486b9e354&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" data-itemshowtype=\"undefined\" target=\"_blank\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/2kzh-HgwNZ0_T6_lmjNqsw</a></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">界面设计感的提升需要从组件优化入手，关注排版、色彩、图标等细节处理。通过选择页面、区分组件、寻找参考、筛选对象并完成复制等实战步骤，积累经验，逐步增强设计感。这种刻意练习虽少有人坚持，但能带来显著提升，帮助设计师在行业中脱颖而出。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI0Njc5NzM5OQ==&amp;mid=2247502202&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=e52e1824dcf3fd441be4cd8486b9e354&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" imgurl=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/g0kpxARkI2SVlPVPibKEXK5jfVLxGOicd4IofbbxHs1Yiaak5D6CaWJkK1Ciajv9bIpuEt791sUp5BUMcnhicib3jLKw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" linktype=\"image\" tab=\"innerlink\" data-itemshowtype=\"undefined\" target=\"_blank\" data-linktype=\"1\"><span class=\"js_jump_icon h5_image_link\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/43c1e02d-e8a8-4824-2bf2-8f45e93a5500/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6872964169381107\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"614\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"501967766\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/43c1e02d-e8a8-4824-2bf2-8f45e93a5500/public\"></span></a>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span leaf=\"\">▌</span><span leaf=\"\">ToB 场景下用户需求挖掘与产品共创</span></span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span><span leaf=\"\"><a style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyODY4MTMyMw==&amp;mid=2247487381&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=82a8c9db8691769f191ece91344261cf&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyODY4MTMyMw==&amp;mid=2247487381&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=82a8c9db8691769f191ece91344261cf&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" data-itemshowtype=\"undefined\" target=\"_blank\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/p-qDR_cDqrLy4I1eur33jA</a></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在ToB场景下，用户需求挖掘与产品共创是产品成功的关键。通过深入理解业务背景、市场情况和竞品研究，明确目标用户并覆盖不同角色，以共创方式挖掘痛点，辨别真需求，并快速验证概念，优化产品设计。最终通过闭环共创，找到用户的Aha Moment，打磨产品细节并推进上线。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyODY4MTMyMw==&amp;mid=2247487381&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=82a8c9db8691769f191ece91344261cf&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" imgurl=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/g0kpxARkI2SVlPVPibKEXK5jfVLxGOicd4k4h5JACpjv4BcHZynnvIK3sfcnn3DRAmlH1nlfWZw9f6ib5zlCNxcWg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" linktype=\"image\" tab=\"innerlink\" data-itemshowtype=\"undefined\" target=\"_blank\" data-linktype=\"1\"><span class=\"js_jump_icon h5_image_link\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9795e766-e5ac-4077-ce98-ebf709406b00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6921824104234527\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"614\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"501967767\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9795e766-e5ac-4077-ce98-ebf709406b00/public\"></span></a>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span leaf=\"\">▌</span><span leaf=\"\">LSM-TREE从入门到入魔：从零开始实现一个高性能键值存储 ｜ 得物技术</span></span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span><span leaf=\"\"><a style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkxNTE3ODU0NA==&amp;mid=2247538072&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=c3506a84400c5cc3c72b2b0ff2291384&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkxNTE3ODU0NA==&amp;mid=2247538072&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=c3506a84400c5cc3c72b2b0ff2291384&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" data-itemshowtype=\"undefined\" target=\"_blank\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/Ghx9emnAnrAhkkcUrqzHjg</a></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">文章介绍了使用Zig语言实现LSM-Tree的过程，涵盖MemTable、SSTable、写入、迭代器、读取和压缩等核心功能。通过实现，作者深入理解了LSM-Tree的多层数据结构和读写流程，同时分享了使用Zig语言开发的经验和心得，包括智能指针的实现和工程实践建议。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkxNTE3ODU0NA==&amp;mid=2247538072&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=c3506a84400c5cc3c72b2b0ff2291384&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" imgurl=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/g0kpxARkI2SVlPVPibKEXK5jfVLxGOicd49AYX1icI9lfu1icq0ofdUkRXVpEZZuicysPqwQ75EAz321nVWTBZRBiajw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" linktype=\"image\" tab=\"innerlink\" data-itemshowtype=\"undefined\" target=\"_blank\" data-linktype=\"1\"><span class=\"js_jump_icon h5_image_link\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e2d4316b-cc98-48da-4125-1b553878b400/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7332053742802304\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"521\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"501967768\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e2d4316b-cc98-48da-4125-1b553878b400/public\"></span></a>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span leaf=\"\">▌</span><span leaf=\"\">万字详解零售支付：支付全景、渠道聚合、支付中台、进件与配置</span></span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span><span leaf=\"\"><a style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg2MTg1NTM4NA==&amp;mid=2247505897&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=863f1eeb2f857c8c561f95164ab58baf&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg2MTg1NTM4NA==&amp;mid=2247505897&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=863f1eeb2f857c8c561f95164ab58baf&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" data-itemshowtype=\"undefined\" target=\"_blank\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/4o0qc1AuGwnyBJ5ZKGG0Dg</a></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">文章深入剖析了新零售支付体系，涵盖支付全景、渠道聚合、支付中台、进件与配置等关键环节。从传统零售到新零售的转变，强调支付在连接用户、商家和平台中的核心作用。详细解读了支付中台的架构设计、功能模块，以及商户进件和支付账号配置的流程，为理解新零售支付提供了全面视角。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg2MTg1NTM4NA==&amp;mid=2247505897&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=863f1eeb2f857c8c561f95164ab58baf&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" imgurl=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/g0kpxARkI2SVlPVPibKEXK5jfVLxGOicd4NT47SZSVQlMWciaicUC5n2ibEhnDbt3ibgPd7hIic49X1CLVlm1brHicQjOg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" linktype=\"image\" tab=\"innerlink\" data-itemshowtype=\"undefined\" target=\"_blank\" data-linktype=\"1\"><span class=\"js_jump_icon h5_image_link\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d764930b-81e5-49cc-d354-aa271eda5d00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9071661237785016\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"614\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"501967769\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d764930b-81e5-49cc-d354-aa271eda5d00/public