=\"614\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"501967770\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bcd844ff-7544-4e84-c52d-7c00b3b5ac00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 48px 0px 0em;padding: 0px;clear: both;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/002df5bd-2056-43e3-68c8-a0876abe3000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.11296296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;vertical-align: bottom;height: 65px;width: 578px;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"65\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/002df5bd-2056-43e3-68c8-a0876abe3000/public\"></span></p>\n  <h2 data-node-type=\"block\" data-block-type=\"text\" style=\"margin: 24px 0px;padding: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;line-height: 2em;\">\n   <section style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n    <span style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"></span></strong></span>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"margin: 24px 0px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n    <span style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span leaf=\"\">▌</span><span leaf=\"\">晚点独家丨美团内部沟通会：食杂零售、国际化、AI 是王兴关注的 “新” 方向</span></span></strong></span>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span><span leaf=\"\"><a style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU3Mjk1OTQ0Ng==&amp;mid=2247524048&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=1a4815bf1ae903660dbcf38d88e2b7e9&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU3Mjk1OTQ0Ng==&amp;mid=2247524048&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=1a4815bf1ae903660dbcf38d88e2b7e9&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" data-itemshowtype=\"undefined\" target=\"_blank\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/tt3TmOrfzRboCJ_Y5ezyRQ</a></span></span>\n   </section><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">美团 CEO 王兴在内部沟通会上提出未来关注的三大新方向：食杂零售、国际化和科技。其中，国际化进展最快，外卖海外版 Keeta 在沙特加速扩张，计划三年内覆盖海湾六国，并考虑进入日韩、北非及拉美等市场。Keeta 通过大额补贴和优化服务快速抢占市场份额，同时美团也在探索利用国内经验降低成本、挖掘用户需求。</span></span>\n   <section style=\"margin: 24px 0px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n    <span style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span leaf=\"\">▌</span><span leaf=\"\">面试玄学？技术招聘反直觉定律：面试问题数量与offer概率成反比</span></span></strong></span>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span><span leaf=\"\">https://solo.xin/topic/2843</span></span>\n   </section><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">文章探讨了技术招聘中一个反直觉现象：面试问题数量与获得offer的概率成反比。分析了背后的三大法则：企业规模决定考核颗粒度，招聘窗口期影响容错阈值，信任系数重塑考核天平。同时，为技术人提供了破局建议，如建立企业情报图谱、准备弹性话术库和设计信任触发点，帮助求职者更好地应对面试。</span></span>\n   <section style=\"margin: 24px 0px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n    <span style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span leaf=\"\">▌</span><span leaf=\"\">DeepSeek来了，我们这个行业会不会被淘汰</span></span></strong></span>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span><span leaf=\"\"><a style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA4OTgxNzM3OQ==&amp;mid=2652581897&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b1d08db09004d3be30f89ecaa935110c&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA4OTgxNzM3OQ==&amp;mid=2652581897&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b1d08db09004d3be30f89ecaa935110c&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" data-itemshowtype=\"undefined\" target=\"_blank\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/9Fk9rf2X9sOJku4rp1MGzg</a></span></span>\n   </section><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">文章探讨了DeepSeek等AI工具对行业的影响，认为AI虽能高效整合信息，但无法替代人类的认知和价值观。重复性、低创造力的工作可能被AI取代，而需要人类经验、情感和复杂决策的工作仍具不可替代性。作者认为，AI是辅助工具，能提升效率，但无法完全替代人类的专业判断和策略制定。</span></span>\n   <section style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"></span>\n   </section></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 48px;margin-bottom: 0em;white-space: normal;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/17788169-5ee5-4d99-0904-262d1ebf8100/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.11296296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 578px;height: 65px;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"65\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/17788169-5ee5-4d99-0904-262d1ebf8100/public\"></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(1, 194, 96);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span leaf=\"\">▌</span><span leaf=\"\">《县委书记们的主政谋略》：揭秘县官的目标与内心世界</span></span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: normal;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">豆瓣评分：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cf71c73b-3478-4cce-b3fe-4f68044f1500/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"75\" style=\"text-align: center;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cf71c73b-3478-4cce-b3fe-4f68044f1500/public\"></span><span style=\"font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: normal;font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;|&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\">7.5</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: normal;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: normal;font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span><span leaf=\"\"><a style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA4NDA3NjY3Mw==&amp;mid=2650628886&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=3960bd30c87b676be78537288d231df7&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA4NDA3NjY3Mw==&amp;mid=2650628886&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=3960bd30c87b676be78537288d231df7&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" data-itemshowtype=\"undefined\" target=\"_blank\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/oSpremcAOg7Nouo1EBejgg</a></span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">《县委书记们的主政谋略》通过对县委书记群体的深入剖析，揭示了他们在主政过程中需要兼顾的多重目标：工作目标、升迁目标、名利目标和安全目标。书中指出，县委书记在施政中既要响应宏观政策，又要面对基层诉求，常在灰色地带谨慎权衡，以实现多目标的平衡。</span></span></section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "本期有意思小周刊汇总了 AI、产品设计、UI 设计等多个热门技术领域文章。",
